📌 Numbered Steps (bottom text translation)

🔹 Japanese:

① 不成立入力後に即時でネオnetの「新契約進捗状況照会」に反映
② 当日に不成立入力した申込を通知対象として夜間に抽出（休日オンライン稼働がある週は金土入力分をまとめて抽出）
③ 募集人宛にプッシュ通知を発信
④ プッシュ通知を受け取り、ネオnetの「新契約進捗状況照会」を参照

⸻

🔸 English:

① Once non-establishment is entered, it is immediately reflected in ネオnet’s “New Contract Progress Status Inquiry.”
② Applications marked as non-established that day are extracted overnight as notification targets.
(In weeks where online services are active over the weekend, entries from Friday and Saturday are grouped together for extraction.)
③ Push notification is sent to the corresponding sales agent.
④ Agent receives the push notification and checks the status in ネオnet.

